This directory contains OpenBM plugin for XBMC as shown in the OpenBM
videos.

module - Contains the python plugin module which is required for the plugin.
script.ibus.bmw - is the actuall XBMC plugin. The openbm.so compiled from
module need to be copied into script.ibus.bmw/resources/lib

install text2wave and paplay if you want the plugin to talk to you ;)


Copy the script.ibus.bmw/autoexec.py into the xbmc directory, so that the plugin
does automatically starts on every XBMC execution.

openbm-xbmc.10.0.patch contains the patch for the XBMC's confluence plugin.
This patch does add additional vertical menus for Radio and OBC control.